\c 3 Shamwari nhatu dzaDhanieri dzinoramba kunamata chifananidzo chaNebhukadhinezari, ndokuiswa muvira romoto 1 Zvino mambo Nebhukadhinezari akaita chifananidzo chendarama; chakanga chakaita mamita makumi mata‑ nhatu pakureba, namamita matanhatu paupamhi; akachimisa pabani reDhura munyika yaBhabhironi. 2 Ipapo mambo Nebhukadhinezari akatuma vanhu kundo‑ kokera machinda navarayiri namadzishe navatongi navachengeti vepfuma nama‑ kurukota navazivi vemirayiro navabati vose vamativi enyika, kuti vauye kumu‑ tambo wokugadzwa kwechifananidzo chakanga chamiswa naNebhukadhinezari. 3 Ipapo machinda navarayiri namadzishe navatongi navachengeti vepfuma nama‑ kurukota navazivi vemirayiro navabati
